      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "text": "Example:",
        "spans": []
      },
      {
        "type": "preformatted",
        "text": "Some cats are tigers.\nSome tigers are animals. \nSo, some cats are animals.",
        "spans": []
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "text": "This might at first seem to be a good argument, but actually it is fallacious because it has the same logical form as the following more obviously invalid argument:",
        "spans": [
